- Props: `value` (required), `disabled?`, `completed?`
- Provides `StepperItemContext`
- `data-slot="stepper-item"`, `data-state="active|inactive"`, `data-completed=""`, `data-disabled=""`
- Horizontal classes: `flex-1 flex-col items-center gap-2`
- Vertical classes: `flex-row items-start gap-3`

### 3. `StepperTrigger` — Clickable step indicator
- Props: standard `<button>` props
- Reads from both contexts; throws if used outside `<StepperItem>`
- Calls `onValueChange(value)` on click; respects `disabled`
- `data-slot="stepper-trigger"`, `data-state`, `data-completed`, `data-disabled`
- Default classes: `size-8 rounded-full border-2` circle with:
  - inactive: `border-muted-foreground/30 text-muted-foreground`
  - `data-[state=active]:border-primary data-[state=active]:bg-primary data-[state=active]:text-primary-foreground`
  - `data-[completed]:border-primary data-[completed]:bg-primary data-[completed]:text-primary-foreground`
  - `focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2`

### 4. `StepperTitle` — Step title
- `<p>` element, `data-slot="stepper-title"`
- `text-sm font-medium leading-none`
- `group-data-[orientation=horizontal]/stepper-item:text-center`

### 5. `StepperDescription` — Step description
- `<p>` element, `data-slot="stepper-description"`
- `text-xs text-muted-foreground`
- `group-data-[orientation=horizontal]/stepper-item:text-center`

### 6. `StepperSeparator` — Visual connector between steps
- `<div>`, reads `orientation` from root context
- `data-slot="stepper-separator"`, `data-orientation`
- Horizontal: `h-px flex-1 self-auto bg-border` (expands between items, aligns via `items-center` on wrapping div)
- Vertical: `ms-4 w-px self-stretch bg-border` (`ms-4` = 16px centers line under `size-8` trigger)

### 7. `StepperContent` — Content panel (active step only)
- Props: `value?` (for standalone use outside `<StepperItem>`)
- Dual usage: reads from `StepperItemContext` when nested inside `<StepperItem>`, falls back to own `value` prop when standalone
- Returns `null` when the resolved value ≠ active step
- Throws if neither item context nor `value` prop is available
- `data-slot="stepper-content"`, `mt-2`

