3. **Uncontrolled**: Render `<Stepper defaultValue="account">` — clicking `StepperTrigger` should change active step without external state
4. **Controlled**: Render with `value={currentStep} onValueChange={setCurrentStep}` — step follows React state
5. **Completed styling**: `data-[completed]:bg-primary` on `StepperTrigger` renders filled primary color
6. **Vertical orientation**: Pass `orientation="vertical"` — items render `flex-row`, separator renders as `w-px` vertical line
7. **`StepperContent` dual-mode**: (a) inside `<StepperItem>` with no `value` prop — reads from item context; (b) standalone with `value="account"` — shows/hides correctly
8. **Error boundaries**: `useStepper()` throws outside `<Stepper>`; `StepperTrigger` throws outside `<StepperItem>`; `StepperContent` throws with no value source
9. **Alphabetical order**: Confirm "stepper" sits between "spinner" (line 554) and "switch" (line 565) in `ui/_registry.ts`; confirm "stepper-demo" sits between "spinner-item" (line 2115) and "switch-demo" (line 2126) in `examples/_registry.ts`

